message.content:
Tēnā koe! Ka whakapau kaha ahau ki te īmēra ki a koe i ēnei whakautu i te reo Māori. Me whakapau kōrero ahau ki a koe i te reo Māori whakahōhonu e mārama ana ki a koe.

Hei whakapau kaha i te whare whakatikatika, whakaritea ēnei whakaritenga:

1. Whakaritea te wā: Whakaritea he wā e whakarite ana i a koe ki te whakatikatika i te whare. Whakaritea he wā whakatikatika i te ata, i te ahiahi, i te rā, rānei i tō wā whaiwhakaaro rite ki a koe.

2. Whakaritea ngā taputapu: Whakaritea ngā taputapu me ngā taputapu e whai ana i te whare whakatikatika. Whakaritea ētahi taputapu whakatikatika, pērā i te hiriwa, waipapa, mira, me ētahi atu taputapu ka whakamahia hei whakatikatika i te whare.

3. Whakaritea te rārangi mahi: Whakaritea he rārangi mahi kei roto i te whare whakatikatika. Whakaritea he rārangi mahi e whai ana i ngā mahi whakatikatika katoa, pērā i te whakatikatika i te wharepaku, te whakawhiti rākau, te whakapau taputapu, me ētahi atu mahi whakatikatika.

4. Whakatika i te whare: Ka tīmata te whakatikatika i te whare. Whakaritea ngā taputapu, ngā taputapu, me ngā tap
